 of Russian descent]]\n[[Category:FCI Levadia Tallinn players]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Belgium]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in Belgium]]\n[[Category:RWDM Brussels FC players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Russia]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in Russia]]\n[[Category:FC Khimki players]]\n[[Category:FC Luch Vladivostok players]]\n[[Category:FC Torpedo Moscow players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Azerbaijan]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in Azerbaijan]]\n[[Category:Azerbaijan Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in Georgia (country)]]\n[[Category:Erovnuli Liga players]]\n[[Category:FC Dinamo Tbilisi players]]\n[[Category:Qingdao Huanghai F.C. players]]\n[[Category:China League One players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in China]]\n[[Category:Estonian expatriate sportspeople in China]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:FCI Tallinn players]]\n[[Category:FC Puuma Tallinn players]]\n[[Category:Neft\u00e7i PFK players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Vladimir Voskoboinikov\n| image          = V-Voskoboinikov.jpg\n| fullname       = Vladimir Voskoboinikov\n| height         = {{height|m=1.88}}\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1983|02|02}}\n| birth_place    = [[Tallinn]], [[Estonia]]\n| position       = [[Forward (association football)#Centre forward|Centre forward]]\n| youthyears1 = 1991\u20132001\n| youthclubs1 = [[FC Puuma Tallinn|Puuma]]\n| years1 = 2001\u20132004 | caps1 = 80 | goals1 = 25 | clubs1 = [[FC Levadia Tallinn|Levadia]]\n| years2 = 2004\u20132006 | caps2 =  8 | goals2 =  0 | clubs2 = [[FC Brussels|Brussels]]\n| years3 = 2005      |